charachters and heavily drain Mutates energy. It wouldnt cause anything to 
break, so the sword/staff thing shall not. Especially since you dont seem to 
realize that the thing could be made of energy itself, a kind of metal, a 
hybrid of the two, or whatnot. You just want to have what you want to happen, 
happen.
